# ==============================================================================
# NPMIGNORE — Files excluded from published package
# ==============================================================================
# Purpose: Controls package contents uploaded to npm to keep tarball minimal.
# Docs: https://docs.npmjs.com/cli/v9/configuring-npm/package-json#files
# ==============================================================================

